videos.description: Baylor's King McClure finds an open Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. for a 2-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Baylor's first points come off a thunderous slam dunk

videos.description: Baylor's Terry Maston feeds Johnathan Motley for a 2-handed slam.
videos.headline: Motley throws down a 2-handed jam

videos.description: Baylor's Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. gets the offensive rebound and finishes with a powerful dunk
videos.headline: Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. dunks with authority

videos.description: Iowa State's Nazareth Mitrou-Long's 3-Pointer is answered by a 3-Pointer from Baylor's Jake Lindsey to take a Baylor 37-36 lead heading into halftime.
videos.headline: Baylor and Iowa State trade 3's and the lead at the of the 1st half

videos.description: Iowa State's Deonte Burton and Baylor's Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. make shots to tie the game at 63.
videos.headline: Baylor and Iowa State hit back-to-back baskets to tie the game late

videos.description: Iowa State's Monte Morris misses a contested jumper at the buzzer to give Baylor a 65-63 win.
videos.headline: Iowa State misses the game-tying buzzer beater

videos.description: Postgame Breakdown of Baylor's last-second 65-63 victory over Iowa State
videos.headline: Postgame Breakdown of Baylor's last-second 65-63 victory over Iowa State

videos.description: Manu Lecomte hits an off-balanced rainbow shot to give No. 2 Baylor the lead with eight seconds on the clock, and the Bears hold on to defeat Iowa State and remain unbeaten on the season.
videos.headline: Baylor holds on against Iowa State to remain unbeaten
